Answer.aesthetic-minimalist: The website design didnt look cluttered as there was not much content given in the website
Answer.comments: It would have been great if there were some videos of the precious moments in the matches , photos of the main achievements of the team included in the website
Answer.consistency-standards: usualy every website has the main data or link to main data from the home page itself like upcoming matches, last matches scorecard ect, which i couldnt find on this site.
Answer.error-prevention: The score card didnt come as expected in the first click, the total scorecard is expected on clicking match info and rest of the details are to be followed by that.
Answer.visibility-system-status: I too found it difficult to actually pinpoint the purpose of the website. the visitor is left in doubt that is this a website of a club, educational institution, college or a page set up by a fan of the team
